The '''Intellex VI''' [[Computer/Legends|computer]] was used by [[R4 astromech droid/Legends|R4-series agromech droids]] and produced by [[Industrial Automaton/Legends|Industrial Automaton]]. It was an improvement on the [[Intellex V/Legends|Intellex V]] brain of the [[R3-series astromech droid/Legends|R3-series]], but was designed for use with [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlift]] vehicles and common commercial space [[Transport/Legends|transports]].<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

